{"tid":1532254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地屌我都係咁講 即使運動失敗 都唔可以無左條命","createTime":"2019-09-02T13:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:03:12.000Z","uid":191568,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3496437e2690fbe3a15573287bec42f4ea832952","tid":1532254,"uid":191568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:05:02.000Z","msg":"警告定先 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你地咪自殺</span><br />\n<br />\n爭取左兩個月 林鄭 黑警變本加厲 有恃無恐<br />\n五大訴求訴到D咩？<br />\n你我大家都洩氣 條氣唔順都要繼續 時間無了期<br />\n甚至見到有人開始想放棄 想死。<br />\n<br />\n而家已經係咁 運動完左輸左 咩都爭取唔到<br />\n想死的人會更多 <br />\n<br />\n但我同你地講定先，<span style=\"color: red;\">咪死呀</span>，輸左又點， 輸左唔係冇出路<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我寧願你地背棄香港 <br />\n移民/長駐外國工作/做難民/working hoilday去外國<br />\n<br />\n可能會得自己一個   係困難 冇人冇物<br />\n但至少你有條命 仲可以做你想做的<br />\n將來亦有機會再見一齊上過街抗爭過的手足！<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AvrCNvW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvrCNvW.png&h=35761e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/czpT5hD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FczpT5hD.png&h=70af8513&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JvfcBpj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJvfcBpj.png&h=8422a31f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"808a30287e3b44f369cb5a2b371948cea860416d","tid":1532254,"uid":761,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"十點鳩叫行動！！！！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Av5cBad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAv5cBad.jpg&h=53535c10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4pT43z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4pT43z.jpg&h=df08fc7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TH9T43A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTH9T43A.jpg&h=5ee30c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=